{"tid":2224944,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"你的生活如何，你的樣子也必如何","createTime":"2020-10-01T02:51:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-01T03:15:06.000Z","uid":376073,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"7aacf625c78ceb66bc83cd68bc7c4ab418543479","tid":2224944,"uid":376073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T02:51:35.000Z","msg":"以前中學有個班花公屋妹，上到大學都係靚女，出到黎社會打份牛工，同個公屋仔一齊，生活得一般，最近再見返佢，殘到嚇親我<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，唔係皮膚，而係生活嘅苦難真係會令一個人愈來愈樣衰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n相反中學明明個樣好普通嘅有錢私樓妹，考唔到大學就去咗外國做abc，每個月唔知用幾多錢打扮自己都算，個樣都完全話咗比人知係生活無憂，成個人唔係話靚咗，而係有光芒<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以話，打份牛工嘅奴隸真係有樣睇呃唔到人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c2a1f461e9f28c1e141b5ab9cf9b88520549fb6","tid":2224944,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T03:04:01.000Z","msg":"何超蓮<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好想知中學小學同學依家咩環境<br />\n係唔係個個都好似我咁慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3198c6016a7b1776a43a4bc20c26fe97b7156e1e","tid":2224944,"uid":376073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1c2a1f461e9f28c1e141b5ab9cf9b88520549fb6","tid":2224944,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T03:04:01.000Z","msg":"何超蓮<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好想知中學小學同學依家咩環境<br />\n係唔係個個都好似我咁慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T03:10:31.000Z","msg":"I know that feel bro <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想辭咗份牛工去樓下做看更算數"},{"pid":"4e4c2867d86e0a6d69e8c1be47e3748f393fb5bd"